messages.messageBody:
I don't intend to announce all the chats on this list at all, but it's
an hour before chat-time, I missed last Friday's chat for being on a
train, and I do intend to chat tonight, my last night in Wales.
Tomorrow I go to Julie Daniel's house in Ashford, Surrey (this side of
London) and I fly home Thursday, so I'll be in the Friday chat from
Albuquerque.

I have a new little 13" MacBook, because I dropped and broke the
screen on my practically new MacBook I bought in January. The
keyboards aren't just the same, so you can see me make Many Typos!
But I can type in � pounds and euros �.


The times:

Two hours, beginning:

Mountain: 3:00 pm
Central: 4:00 pm
Eastern: 5:00 pm
England: 10:00 pm Monday

Pune, India: 2:30 am Tuesday
